snippet.title: Casey Donovan on tour and visiting Wollongong
snippet.content:
Queen of the Jungle, Casey Donovan on 'I'm A Celebrity Get Me Out of Here'. Picture: Network 10 Appearing on I'm A Celebrity Get Me Out of Here (and subsequently winning the competition) seemed to propel singer Casey Donovan back into the spotlight. The former Australian Idol winner turned Uber driver is on tour and bringing her sounds to Centro CBD in Wollongong on October 20. It comes as the 29-year-old released a new single, "The Villain", in July - a song penned about the darkness of anxiety.
